ScriptName fbmwGothrenScript

BEGIN OnHit Player
	mwGothredDremoraGuard1.SetAV Aggression 100
	mwGothredDremoraGuard1.ModDisposition Player -100
	mwGothredDremoraGuard1.StartCombat Player
	mwGothredDremoraGuard2.SetAV Aggression 100
	mwGothredDremoraGuard2.ModDisposition Player -100
	mwGothredDremoraGuard2.StartCombat Player
END

BEGIN OnDeath
	if ( GetStage fbmwMQTelvanniGothren >= 1 && GetStage fbmwMQTelvanniGothren < 100 )
		SetStage fbmwMQTelvanniGothren 100
	endif

	SET fbmwMQTelvanni.HortVotes TO fbmwMQTelvanni.HortVotes + 1
	mwMallamRyonREF.Disable

	mwGothredDremoraGuard1.SetAV Aggression 100
	mwGothredDremoraGuard1.ModDisposition Player -100
	mwGothredDremoraGuard1.StartCombat Player

	mwGothredDremoraGuard2.SetAV Aggression 100
	mwGothredDremoraGuard2.ModDisposition Player -100
	mwGothredDremoraGuard2.StartCombat Player

	mwBrolmirREF.SetAV Aggression 100
	mwBrolmirREF.ModDisposition Player -100
	mwBrolmirREF.StartCombat Player

	mwEndaseAvelREF.SetAV Aggression 100
	mwEndaseAvelREF.ModDisposition Player -100
	mwEndaseAvelREF.StartCombat Player
END
